Package: PAMwheelR
Title: Visualization of PAM Sequences as Wheel Diagrams
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yu", "Donglin", email = "yudonglin@stu.pku.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates wheel diagram visualizations of PAM sequences with multiple layers,
    showing the relative frequencies of different bases at each position.
